256
0:11:15.26,000 --> 0:11:18,000
"Peut-être que si j'arrive sous un angle différent."

257
0:11:19.26,000 --> 0:11:22,000
(Rires)

258
0:11:22.26,000 --> 0:11:24,000
Non.

259
0:11:24.26,000 --> 0:11:27,000
